<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1437,1374,2005]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,419,1374,1398]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">Description of the adult</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[434,537,1374,1397]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 4. 1 – 2" captionStartId="1.[151,270,1949,1973]" captionTargetBox="[166,1417,197,1925]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[166,1420,197,1926]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 4. 1 – 2 Adult of Amblystira niborskiana sp. n. 1, Dorsal view. Scale bar: 1 mm; 2, Rostral channel. Scale bar: 0.5 mm. 3 – 4 Fifth instar of Amblystira niborskiana sp. n. 3, Dorsal view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm; 4, Lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/199189/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Figs. 
<number box="[495,537,1374,1397]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1–2</number>
</figureCitation>
). General coloration black except for a narrow hyaline space on the costal area, legs and segments I, II, III and base of IV yellowish. Body beneath black. Body length: 3.00- 
<number box="[1094,1143,1406,1429]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="2.9">2.90</number>
-3.00.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1437,1374,2005]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Head short, shiny; with five spines, frontal and anterior pair very short and decumbent; occipital pair stout, decumbent and long reaching anterior margin of eye. Eyes dark red. Bucculae wide, wider posteriorly, at its maximum width with four rows of areolae. Head length: 
<number box="[528,632,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.22" valueMax="0.23" valueMin="0.21">0.21-0.23</number>
- 
<number box="[640,688,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.21">0.21</number>
; width: 
<number box="[775,824,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.41">0.41</number>
- 
<number box="[831,880,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.41">0.41</number>
- 
<number box="[887,936,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.41">0.41</number>
. Antennal segments measurements: 
<number box="[1326,1374,1502,1525]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.13">0.13</number>
- 
<number pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.12" valueMax="0.13" valueMin="0.11">0.11- 0.13</number>
: 
<number box="[213,263,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.1">0.10</number>
- 
<number box="[269,375,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.09" valueMax="0.1" valueMin="0.08">0.08-0.10</number>
: 
<number box="[385,434,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.98">0.98</number>
- 
<number box="[442,547,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.905" valueMax="0.93" valueMin="0.88">0.88-0.93</number>
: 
<number box="[558,663,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.475" valueMax="0.48" valueMin="0.47">0.47-0.48</number>
- 
<number box="[670,720,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.5">0.50</number>
; proportions 
<number box="[861,910,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.08">0.08</number>
- 
<number box="[918,967,1534,1557]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.08">0.08</number>
